name: An aura of dignity
description:
She was alone, just as always she was drunk from this loneliness! 
The master of speaking is in silence and has gone through all the tragedies of her life alone. 
Now, the whiteness of her hair shows the hardships of war with the times
And each of the lines on her face is a memory of joy and sorrow on the hectic path of life
And now what is left for her is her God and a bag of nostalgia.
She always tells me that no school is higher than experience, but alas, its tuition is as expensive as a lifetime ...!
